# --- Ignore everything by default ---
*

# --- Keep repository metadata ---
!.gitignore
!README.md

# --- Keep outward-facing guide docs ---
!docs/
!docs/**

# --- Keep your HPC Python scripts ---
!hpc_python/
!hpc_python/**

# --- Keep your HPC LSF scripts ---
!hpc_lsf/
!hpc_lsf/**

# --- Keep lightweight environment documentation ---
!envs/
!envs/README.md

# --- Keep reusable thesis templates ---
!thesis_templates/
!thesis_templates/**

# --- Ignore large or irrelevant content ---
data/
results/
envs/
miniconda3/
Reference_genomes_and_databases/
humann_project/
kneaddata_project/
**/*.fastq*
**/*.fq
**/*.bam
**/*.sam
**/*.gz
**/*.tar*
**/*.zip
**/*.log

# --- Keep only lightweight env documentation, not large env artifacts ---
!envs/
!envs/README.md
